	dprr:hasNoteText "Celebrated on coins as the first to put on the Floralia, perhaps as a regular festival (Grueber, CRRBM 1.469f.; cf. Ovid Fast. 5.329-330, and above, on Consuls; see 241, Aediles of the Plebs; Seidel 37; Cesano, Stud. Num. 1.201f.)." ;
